---
description: AI development workflow, planning artifacts, and review gates
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` before changing files. It is the repository operating
contract for AI agents.

Use this workflow:

```text
shape-work -> dispatch-wave when useful -> tdd -> implement -> polish -> review-pr -> human approval -> retro-pr
```

Durable planning artifacts live under `thoughts/shared/`.

The canonical reusable skill instructions live in:

```text
~/.agents/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md
```

For repo-specific behavior, prefer updating `AGENTS.md` or adding a
repo-local skill under `.agents/skills/`.
